 of gold trainers.\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As boats filled with athletes sailed down the river Seine, Snoop Dogg stood in the drizzle alongsideThe Today Showhost Hoda Kotb to interview Biles family.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1072, \"end\": 1082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}, {\"begin\": 1132, \"end\": 1141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hoda Kotb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles, 27, who is the most decorated gymnast in Olympic history with four gold medals, was noticeably absent from Team USA's boat to rest up ahead of Sunday's women's qualifier, mom Nellie Biles said.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1284, \"end\": 1292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9999420382228101, \"rank\": 5.246377075588706e-05, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The gymnast looks to scoop up her fifth gold medal this week.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1433, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it wasn't thefirst time Snoop Dogghas met Biles' mother with the rapper apparently making Nellie and Simone wait on him during a meeting in 2010.\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Snoop, I do not know if you know this, but Simone and you have known each other for a long time.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Right, Nellie?\\\"\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1704, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kotb revealed.\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Initially perplexed, Snoop Dogg retorted: \\\"How?\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1742, \"end\": 1752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How, Nellie?\\\"\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nellie Biles said that the West Coast rapper had met the family in Times Square in New York City in 2010 -six years prior to Biles' Olympic debut.\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1867, \"end\": 1880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 7.392732821320637e-12, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said that the family wanted to grab a photograph with Snoop Dogg.\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 2000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1989, \"end\": 1999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And you said - 'cause we asked for a picture - two minutes.\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2062, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One, two, and you were gone,\\\" she revealed.\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The group laughed off the incident.\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Sunday, Snoop Dogg was seen sporting a white tracksuit shrouded in the star-spangled banner and a T-shirt of the gymnast's face as he watchedBiles and the rest of Team USA's gymnastics teamcompete at Bercy Arena.\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2156, \"end\": 2166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}, {\"begin\": 2311, \"end\": 2319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9999420382228101, \"rank\": 5.246377075588706e-05, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other stars including Tom Cruise and Lady Gaga also sat in the crowd as the team emerged in leotards adorned with thousands of crystals, each outfit costing $3,000.\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2384, \"end\": 2394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 2399, \"end\": 2408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite a minor calf tweak and walking with a limp, the routine earned Biles a 14.600 and an impressive total of 59.566, guaranteeing her a spot in the finals next week in all four individual events.\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2727, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She came first in her division on both the vault and floor, second on the beam and eighth on uneven bars.\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2834, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The centrepiece was the vault where Biles set a score of 15.300 - almost a full point ahead of American teammate Jade Carey.\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2960, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2931, \"end\": 2939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.996652954199859, \"rank\": 0.00287328277531307, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2949, \"end\": 2959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jade Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It marked a major return for Biles after a 732-day hiatus from major competitions after she pulled out of the TokyoOlympicsin 2021 to prioritize her mental health.\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 3125, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Day one, now moving on to team finals, all-around finals, a couple event finals hopefully,\\\" US coach Cecile Landi said.\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3220, \"end\": 3222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9174114056597914, \"rank\": 0.06645428053632355, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The US team is looking to take gold on Tuesday before athletes start the individual event finals on Thursday.\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3358, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3253, \"end\": 3255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9174114056597914, \"rank\": 0.06645428053632355, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles is vying to become the oldest American women to win an Olympic gold in gymnastics.\", \"from\": 3360, \"to\": 3448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3396, \"end\": 3404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.996652954199859, \"rank\": 0.00287328277531307, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3450, \"to\": 3680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3501, \"end\": 3512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.74375761664837e-16, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"